data.description: Welcome to your new home! Presenting a gorgeous 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath end unit townhome that's sure to capture your heart.  Step inside to discover the beauty and numerous updated features, creating a welcoming atmosphere throughout. With a spacious layout, this home offers ample room for both relaxation and entertainment.  Indulge in the luxury of a large primary suite, providing a private retreat for ultimate comfort and tranquility. Need a space for remote work or creative endeavors? You're in luck! This townhome features a versatile flex room, perfect for use as a home office or whatever suits your lifestyle.  Enjoy the convenience of a well-appointed kitchen with all appliances included, making family dinners a breeze. Plus, never worry about parking with your very own 1-car garage. Convenient to interstate, airport and the Tanger Outlet Mall. Don't let this home pass you by. Priced to sell.
